flowchart TD
  A[Change idea] --> B[Prediction]
  B --> C[Customer approval]
  C --> D[Deploy new version]
  D --> E[Track behavior]
  E --> F[Compare before/after]
  F --> G{Result}
  G -- Better --> H[Winner pattern]
  G -- Worse --> I[Rollback or new test]
  G -- Unclear --> J[Observe]
  H --> K[Roll out to similar pages]
